surestimé passant apres le tres moyen wild mood swings , ce bloodflowers a eu droit a plein d'eloges , mais ca reste un album tres moyen , manquant de profondeur , et ne prenant jamais aux tripes comme un bon album de the cure est censé le faire . tout est trop gentil et trop mou . heureusement l'album eponyme sorti en 2004 a recitifé le tir de fort belle maniere . ||| overestimated after passing through the very wild mood swings , this bloodflowers was right full of praise , but it 's still a very average album , lacking depth , and never taking the guts to be a good album of the cure is supposed to . everything is too nice and too soft . fortunately the self-titled album released in 2004 recitifé shooting very beautiful way .